@startuml
title Gmail Sequence

participant Application
participant GmailClient
participant Gmail

Application -> GmailClient: connect()
GmailClient -> Gmail: IMAP SSL login
Gmail --> GmailClient: success
Application -> GmailClient: fetch_unread()
GmailClient -> Gmail: search UNSEEN
Gmail --> GmailClient: messages
Application -> GmailClient: mark_processed()
GmailClient -> Gmail: add label / mark seen

@enduml
